2. Primitive objects

Let:
	•	s_t = state at time t
	•	a_t = action at time t
	•	f_t = feedback received after action
	•	c_t = constraint field at time t
	•	b_t = break event or stress test at time t
	•	I_t = intelligence state at time t

Intelligence is not identical to performance.
